        "subject": "LU-4647 tests: enable sanity-sec for DNE mode",
        "message": "LU-4647 tests: enable sanity-sec for DNE mode\n\nAllow sanity-sec to run with multiple MDS nodes.  While this patch\ndoes not necessarily actively run tests on mutiple MDTs, at least it\nwould no longer be skipped when multiple MDSes are configured.  This\nwill double test coverage, prevent potential regressions, and would\nallow future tests to verify DNE functionality more easily.\n\nClean up code style (tabs for indent, $(...) instead of `...`, etc).\n\nTest-Parameters: alwaysuploadlogs envdefinitions=SLOW=yes \\\nmdtcount=4 testlist=sanity-sec\n\nTest-Parameters: alwaysuploadlogs envdefinitions=SLOW=yes \\\nmdtcount=1 testlist=sanity-sec\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I81a2e84fd96097c933c58174cb797fe6b18cab07\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
